{"tid":506572,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人聽過腸漏症？","createTime":"2017-12-22T10:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T06:11:41.000Z","uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cab61badbc7b67e166922769b3ad1fe8fd9ac3e5","tid":506572,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"上網睇佢話唔算係一種病，唔見有專科睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係小腸牆壁受到破壞，啲食物未消化晒就進入血液，引發一連串食物過敏，網上教路有一堆方法，主要係戒糖、奶製品同碳水化合物一段時間，補充品有三隻：L-glutamine, omega 3同digestive enzymes<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同IBS都幾似喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4625736bf21aab0e144bdf134b72e6a0047ab6de","tid":506572,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"自律神經失調 個類野?"},{"pid":"a72ab415567aba058e9694e430f9d16afb8b5e5e","tid":506572,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:53:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自律神經失調 個類野?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係腸漏症其中一個後果，因為腸道出問題亂咁俾未消化好的食物份子入血，有啲嘢唔應該出現嚮血液，刺激免疫系統做嘢，引起各種過敏反應，你講呢個係其中一種"},{"pid":"9b64ed04fc9d3d791ed868cec978727cb6c920df","tid":506572,"uid":8033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"你有咩病徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1382aff1bbfc0c49fc68d3ffda0224e7a8344a","tid":506572,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有咩病徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食飯後感受到佢入面消化得好吃力，晚餐更明顯，即係遲遲未落格咁，其他症狀：失眠、多暗瘡、便秘、冇精力、耳鳴、焦慮"},{"pid":"494e48d04569946f9b8691bedd0d85314397d5d3","tid":506572,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:17:49.000Z","msg":"英文叫leaky gut，有幾種可能成因，都係長期性：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食太多junk food、加工食品<br />\n<br />\n情緒同壓力<br />\n<br />\n體內重金屬多<br />\n<br />\n曾經食過太多坑生素"},{"pid":"2cc4be89900e0508209fe877a2e09e77f0c01989","tid":506572,"uid":122211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:20:01.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f0e71a8a88d5ef2158722a2bcd0f4102e443080a","tid":506572,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T12:11:48.000Z","msg":"腸胃差已經好撚慘 你個病仲撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c954d2c6726de60f244b7b09321b21e42b85d52c","tid":506572,"uid":11876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T13:03:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腸胃差已經好撚慘 你個病仲撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係一個病黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多只可以叫syndrome<br />\n其實都係腸胃差既一種"},{"pid":"1b54fb8b34350753e380a2eedf1789219d2410f4","tid":506572,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T13:19:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>腸胃差已經好撚慘 你個病仲撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係一個病黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多只可以叫syndrome<br />\n其實都係腸胃差既一種</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講得岩，要靠戒口去俾時間條腸好返，加上食某啲營養補充劑"},{"pid":"72d75b297c0cbfa0911ae79405b8ffccca177f11","tid":506572,"uid":159246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>腸胃差已經好撚慘 你個病仲撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係一個病黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多只可以叫syndrome<br />\n其實都係腸胃差既一種</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講得岩，要靠戒口去俾時間條腸好返，加上食某啲營養補充劑</blockquote><br />\n係咪冇藥醫， 之前試過入院打抗生素針， 我估我都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}